1
00:00:00,440 --> 00:00:01,840
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,840 --> 00:00:03,540
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,540 --> 00:00:05,010
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:11,250 --> 00:00:12,520
(Episode 58)

5
00:00:50,720 --> 00:00:52,860
Help me become
part of the Adele family.

6
00:00:54,030 --> 00:00:55,060
Open the door for me.

7
00:00:55,630 --> 00:00:56,630
I...

8
00:00:59,930 --> 00:01:02,030
I need to become the owner of Adele.

9
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:04,640
What?

10
00:01:05,700 --> 00:01:08,310
If I can't take
Chairman Park Tae Ho's life,

11
00:01:09,540 --> 00:01:11,980
I'll take Adele,
what he loves more than life itself.

12
00:01:14,050 --> 00:01:15,050
You're...

13
00:01:16,110 --> 00:01:17,580
going to take over Adele?

14
00:01:18,850 --> 00:01:21,820
That's why I need to be your wife...

15
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:25,090
and Chairman Park Tae Ho's
daughter-in-law.

16
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:30,130
Your father's walls are so high,
I can't get in from the outside.

17
00:01:31,260 --> 00:01:34,500
But you were never interested
in Adele to begin with.

18
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:39,900
Give me everything you have.
Your family name, your title,

19
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:41,910
and even your shares.

20
00:01:44,180 --> 00:01:45,680
In return, you'll get
the marriage you want...

21
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:47,250
and...

22
00:01:49,950 --> 00:01:51,320
me.

23
00:01:55,720 --> 00:01:56,720
So for you,

24
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:03,190
it's been about revenge
from the very beginning.

25
00:02:05,230 --> 00:02:06,230
Were you...

26
00:02:08,700 --> 00:02:10,770
just planning on using my feelings
to your advantage?

27
00:02:13,770 --> 00:02:17,310
Did you ever once consider
how much pain I'd be in...

28
00:02:19,940 --> 00:02:21,250
after finding out
this horrible truth?

29
00:02:22,980 --> 00:02:25,750
Do you have any idea
how much I love you?

30
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:36,160
I guess my feelings...

31
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:40,060
never mattered to you at all.

32
00:02:40,930 --> 00:02:42,700
But you're no different, are you?

33
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:46,170
You put
your own feelings first, too.

34
00:02:47,670 --> 00:02:51,180
Have you ever once thought about
how I must have felt...

35
00:02:51,410 --> 00:02:52,910
after I lost my dad?

36
00:02:58,280 --> 00:03:00,390
(The late Baek Jun Gi,
The late Baek Jin Ju)

37
00:03:03,890 --> 00:03:06,460
After your father
brutally murdered mine,

38
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:10,300
I had to watch him
live his life with a smile.

39
00:03:10,700 --> 00:03:14,630
I had to watch Choi Yu Na
and Park Tae Ho plot to kill me!

40
00:03:18,640 --> 00:03:21,740
I had to watch the revenge
I spent seven years preparing for...

41
00:03:22,710 --> 00:03:27,110
get completely shattered!

42
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:41,190
Did you...

43
00:03:41,930 --> 00:03:44,430
ever once think about
what was going through my mind...

44
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,760
when I came to you?

45
00:03:54,970 --> 00:03:58,510
I know it won't be easy
abandoning your father.

46
00:03:59,140 --> 00:04:03,180
But then again,
abandoning me won't be easy either.

47
00:04:11,190 --> 00:04:14,560
I know it's a difficult
and painful decision.

48
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:17,900
But still,
you have to make a choice.

49
00:04:18,700 --> 00:04:20,160
It's cruel,

50
00:04:20,630 --> 00:04:22,900
but as Chairman Park Tae Ho's son,

51
00:04:23,430 --> 00:04:25,000
it's a choice you can't escape.

52
00:04:58,170 --> 00:05:00,270
Park Min Jun and Park Hyun Jun.

53
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:05,510
It must be such a heavy burden
for both of them...

54
00:05:06,580 --> 00:05:08,080
to be born as Park Tae Ho's sons.

55
00:05:11,780 --> 00:05:13,050
I'm being...

56
00:05:13,850 --> 00:05:15,920
so cruel to two innocent people,

57
00:05:16,450 --> 00:05:17,920
aren't I?

58
00:05:20,390 --> 00:05:21,960
The wickedness of the people...

59
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:24,060
who tried to harm you
and the innocent Dr. Baek...

60
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,330
is what's cruel.

61
00:06:00,770 --> 00:06:01,770
Mother.

62
00:06:03,070 --> 00:06:04,070
Min Jun.

63
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:06,700
Why are you here?

64
00:06:07,510 --> 00:06:09,240
- I...
- You locked the door too.

65
00:06:11,180 --> 00:06:13,280
I came to see Hyun Jun,

66
00:06:14,410 --> 00:06:16,280
but I didn't realize
the door was locked.

67
00:06:17,010 --> 00:06:18,050
To see Hyun Jun?

68
00:06:18,950 --> 00:06:19,950
Yes.

69
00:06:20,620 --> 00:06:22,450
The chairman sent me on an errand.

70
00:06:22,990 --> 00:06:26,660
I had a message for Hyun Jun
about his marriage.

71
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:27,930
But...

72
00:06:29,060 --> 00:06:30,700
it seems he left early.

73
00:06:31,030 --> 00:06:32,830
I guess I'll just have to
talk to him later.

74
00:06:35,700 --> 00:06:36,700
Mother.

75
00:06:40,670 --> 00:06:42,810
How exactly did
my car accident happen?

76
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:46,810
Why ask that all of a sudden?

77
00:06:47,010 --> 00:06:48,550
It's about the circumstances
of the accident,

78
00:06:48,610 --> 00:06:50,650
and you've said so little
about the past...

79
00:06:50,650 --> 00:06:52,250
that I can't remember.

80
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:57,190
I'm just following
the doctor's advice.

81
00:06:57,860 --> 00:07:01,290
He said it was better
not to tell you directly about your past,

82
00:07:01,390 --> 00:07:04,360
and we should wait for your memories
to return naturally.

83
00:07:05,030 --> 00:07:07,060
Is that why you said
you didn't know Chloe?

84
00:07:08,030 --> 00:07:09,030
What?

85
00:07:09,100 --> 00:07:12,470
She's the one Hyun Jun is marrying.
You must have heard her name.

86
00:07:14,370 --> 00:07:16,870
Were you pretending
you didn't know her?

87
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:21,850
She just wasn't important enough
to explain to you.

88
00:07:23,180 --> 00:07:24,180
I was just worried...

89
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:29,850
that telling you too much
would be a burden on you.

90
00:07:31,460 --> 00:07:32,790
As your mother,

91
00:07:34,130 --> 00:07:38,330
I don't want to see you struggling
with those headaches again.

92
00:07:41,330 --> 00:07:43,840
Let's not try so hard to remember.

93
00:07:44,170 --> 00:07:45,270
All right?

94
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:48,570
Yes, I understand.

95
00:08:02,890 --> 00:08:06,490
I hope I don't have to tell him
about Chloe.

96
00:08:07,730 --> 00:08:10,330
Is he only this curious
because of Hyun Jun's wedding?

97
00:08:15,930 --> 00:08:19,670
Min Jun,
please just give me some time.

98
00:08:20,840 --> 00:08:25,010
So when your memory returns,
it won't be too hard on you.

99
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:28,450
I will take care of anything
that could threaten you...

100
00:08:28,810 --> 00:08:30,650
or make you uncomfortable.

101
00:08:35,550 --> 00:08:38,660
So this is a strand
of Park Hyun Jun's hair?

102
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:41,930
Yes. I found it in Hyun Jun's room.

103
00:08:42,290 --> 00:08:44,000
Any luck with Mr. Song?

104
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:47,000
Right here.

105
00:08:48,100 --> 00:08:50,740
I got him completely flustered
and then swiped it.

106
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:55,240
- Then get it tested right away.
- Okay.

107
00:09:00,140 --> 00:09:02,250
(BIT Life, President Kim Myung Hui)

108
00:09:03,950 --> 00:09:06,520
- I'll be going now.
- Okay.

109
00:09:13,260 --> 00:09:14,330
What can I do for you?

110
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:16,530
I'm...

111
00:09:17,860 --> 00:09:20,430
here to discuss a matter
concerning Min Jun.

112
00:09:22,630 --> 00:09:25,640
You and Chloe were
in the accident together.

113
00:09:27,270 --> 00:09:28,270
What?

114
00:09:29,010 --> 00:09:31,340
You're saying I was
in the accident with Chloe?

115
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:35,310
And you're saying both of us
lost our memories because of it?

116
00:09:35,850 --> 00:09:36,850
Yes.

117
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:40,650
With both victims losing memories
simultaneously,

118
00:09:41,290 --> 00:09:43,350
our investigation has been facing
many difficulties.

119
00:09:45,660 --> 00:09:49,830
We confirmed the accident details
through Chairman Park of Adele.

120
00:09:51,060 --> 00:09:52,460
It seems Chloe...

121
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:55,970
tried to leak secrets to a rival,
but failed.

122
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,040
Chloe did?

123
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:01,140
That's all the information
we have at this time.

124
00:10:01,870 --> 00:10:02,870
Have a good day.

125
00:10:09,050 --> 00:10:12,320
Chloe's the type of person
to leak company secrets?

126
00:10:12,580 --> 00:10:16,250
Is that why Mom didn't say anything?

127
00:10:17,860 --> 00:10:21,060
Is that why everyone was
against her marrying Hyun Jun?

128
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:29,700
- She told him about Chloe?
- Yes. If I hadn't stopped her,

129
00:10:29,770 --> 00:10:32,100
she would've told him
they were in the accident together.

130
00:10:33,370 --> 00:10:36,910
To keep Min Jun's memory as it is,
you need to get a handle on Ms. Oh.

131
00:10:37,680 --> 00:10:39,440
I already spoke to her,

132
00:10:40,180 --> 00:10:41,850
but I don't think it'll do any good.

133
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:45,080
I'll be on my way.

134
00:10:47,220 --> 00:10:49,590
(BIT Life, President Kim Myung Hui)

135
00:10:52,260 --> 00:10:53,360
Oh Jung Ran.

136
00:10:54,290 --> 00:10:56,560
So that's why Min Jun
asked me about her.

137
00:10:57,760 --> 00:11:01,300
She tried to kill my Min Jun
and made him lose his memory,

138
00:11:02,500 --> 00:11:04,500
and now she's trying
to torment him again.

139
00:11:12,710 --> 00:11:15,850
You're showing your face here
practically every day now.

140
00:11:16,980 --> 00:11:19,050
Is this another one of your schemes
to kill me?

141
00:11:19,520 --> 00:11:21,790
Hoping that your face
will make me die of rage?

142
00:11:21,790 --> 00:11:22,790
You'd better...

143
00:11:23,690 --> 00:11:25,890
watch your mouth
in front of Min Jun.

144
00:11:26,590 --> 00:11:28,890
He already lost his memory
because of you.

145
00:11:29,990 --> 00:11:33,130
If you upset him
by spouting nonsense,

146
00:11:34,370 --> 00:11:35,470
I won't let it slide.

147
00:11:35,870 --> 00:11:37,470
It won't just be the chairman.

148
00:11:37,540 --> 00:11:39,970
I'll use your own son
to make you pay.

149
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:43,840
What? You'll use my son?

150
00:11:46,510 --> 00:11:49,410
What if your son gets hurt again
in the process?

151
00:11:50,280 --> 00:11:52,780
Then I'll just have to tell
your son...

152
00:11:53,650 --> 00:11:56,390
who it was that tried
to hurt Min Jun.

153
00:11:57,690 --> 00:11:58,860
Clearly.

154
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:18,580
The son of a cold-blooded murderer.

155
00:12:22,650 --> 00:12:24,620
That man who's my father,

156
00:12:26,850 --> 00:12:28,090
and my mother...

157
00:12:33,060 --> 00:12:34,430
So that's what makes me...

158
00:12:36,030 --> 00:12:37,030
You...

159
00:12:37,800 --> 00:12:40,660
always chose to look away
at the very last moment.

160
00:12:41,970 --> 00:12:43,800
The truth you would
have had to face...

161
00:12:45,100 --> 00:12:46,500
must have been terrifying.

162
00:12:51,180 --> 00:12:54,310
Are you going to run away
and hide this time too?

163
00:12:55,450 --> 00:12:56,610
Is that why...

164
00:12:59,080 --> 00:13:00,990
I became such a coward?

165
00:13:16,130 --> 00:13:18,300
Hey, what are you spacing out about?

166
00:13:18,940 --> 00:13:20,400
That was a close call.

167
00:13:33,920 --> 00:13:36,720
You must have a lot on your mind
with the wedding, right?

168
00:13:38,260 --> 00:13:40,820
How did you fall for someone
like Chloe anyway?

169
00:13:44,630 --> 00:13:46,060
Someone like Chloe?

170
00:13:47,430 --> 00:13:50,000
She doesn't seem like
a very nice person.

171
00:13:52,470 --> 00:13:53,470
Sure.

172
00:13:54,710 --> 00:13:56,170
I guess you could say that.

173
00:13:58,140 --> 00:14:00,580
She has a way
of really hurting people.

174
00:14:03,210 --> 00:14:04,220
Maybe that's why...

175
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:13,160
Right now, I actually envy you.

176
00:14:14,290 --> 00:14:17,090
But I lost my memory.
What's there to envy?

177
00:14:17,900 --> 00:14:21,670
I can't even ask you
how you endured this brutal truth...

178
00:14:24,800 --> 00:14:27,170
since you alone are at peace,
having forgotten it all.

179
00:14:33,780 --> 00:14:35,310
So instead of taking
Chairman Park's life,

180
00:14:35,880 --> 00:14:38,680
you'll take away Adele Group,
what he loves more than life itself?

181
00:14:40,350 --> 00:14:43,650
I'm relieved you decided
against bloodshed,

182
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:46,390
but this marriage
to Park Hyun Jun...

183
00:14:47,260 --> 00:14:48,590
still doesn't sit right with me.

184
00:14:48,860 --> 00:14:52,700
I can't take over Adele Group
from the outside.

185
00:14:53,260 --> 00:14:56,500
As an outsider,
I'm just easily cast aside.

186
00:14:57,200 --> 00:15:01,810
But if I become his daughter-in-law,
a member of the Adele family,

187
00:15:03,810 --> 00:15:05,140
I can hold my ground.

188
00:15:06,180 --> 00:15:09,780
Plus, as Park Hyun Jun's wife,
I'll have a claim in the succession.

189
00:15:10,380 --> 00:15:11,380
True.

190
00:15:12,150 --> 00:15:16,750
- That's true, but...
- I want Chairman Park to suffer...

191
00:15:17,890 --> 00:15:20,090
in the most painful way
for what he's done.

192
00:15:20,790 --> 00:15:24,730
He's a man who uses his own children
for the sake of Adele Group.

193
00:15:25,430 --> 00:15:28,100
If he loses Adele Group to betrayal
of one of his own children,

194
00:15:28,730 --> 00:15:32,000
it'll be that much more
painful for him.

195
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:36,040
And as for Oh Jung Ran,
who tried to hurt Min Jun,

196
00:15:36,940 --> 00:15:38,880
this marriage will be
torture for her, too.

197
00:15:40,210 --> 00:15:43,450
But do you think that
Park Hyun Jun fellow...

198
00:15:44,150 --> 00:15:45,750
will actually step up and help you?

199
00:15:46,580 --> 00:15:48,550
Now that he knows about
his father's crimes,

200
00:15:48,950 --> 00:15:50,490
he won't be able to
turn a blind eye.

201
00:15:50,920 --> 00:15:54,490
Park Hyun Jun is nothing
like his father.

202
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:57,330
Until Park Hyun Jun
makes up his mind,

203
00:15:58,000 --> 00:16:00,930
we'll get ready to meet
with Chairman Park.

204
00:16:02,270 --> 00:16:03,270
All right.

205
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:06,340
Let's play the card
we've been holding for so long.

206
00:16:08,070 --> 00:16:10,640
It's time for James Lee,

207
00:16:11,140 --> 00:16:14,240
the CEO of the investment firm,
JKL Partners, to make his move.

208
00:16:14,710 --> 00:16:16,080
I'm going with you.

209
00:16:16,880 --> 00:16:17,880
Okay.

210
00:16:30,460 --> 00:16:32,000
For goodness sake.

211
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:34,570
What am I going to do
with this girl?

212
00:16:34,800 --> 00:16:39,400
You think acting like Jin Ju
will make Park Min Jun fall for you?

213
00:16:39,470 --> 00:16:43,970
She's right, Yu Na.
I think this is going too far.

214
00:16:44,780 --> 00:16:47,980
Seriously,
what are you going to do...

215
00:16:47,980 --> 00:16:49,480
if Park Min Jun gets
his memory back?

216
00:16:49,680 --> 00:16:52,320
Even the doctor doesn't know
when his memory will return.

217
00:16:53,220 --> 00:16:55,620
And even if it does come back,
I don't care.

218
00:16:56,690 --> 00:16:57,720
Before that happens,

219
00:16:58,460 --> 00:17:01,090
I just have to make him
fall completely for me.

220
00:17:02,590 --> 00:17:04,930
I'm telling you, this is just wrong.
You hear me?

221
00:17:05,530 --> 00:17:09,700
I can't just watch my daughter
live as an imitation of a dead girl.

222
00:17:09,770 --> 00:17:12,470
So what if I am?
All that matters is that I'm happy.

223
00:17:12,800 --> 00:17:14,040
What? What did you just say?

224
00:17:15,540 --> 00:17:17,810
So you're happy now?

225
00:17:18,740 --> 00:17:23,010
Park Min Jun holds my hand,
and he relies on me.

226
00:17:24,650 --> 00:17:27,050
For the first time,
he's actually smiling at me.

227
00:17:28,290 --> 00:17:32,020
He's finally giving me the look
he used to only give Baek Jin Ju.

228
00:17:33,190 --> 00:17:34,430
What are we going to do...

229
00:17:35,730 --> 00:17:36,730
Good grief...

230
00:17:38,800 --> 00:17:40,860
I came first before Baek Jin Ju.

231
00:17:41,570 --> 00:17:44,470
I liked him first,
and I've waited all this time.

232
00:17:46,800 --> 00:17:48,170
So for once,

233
00:17:48,970 --> 00:17:51,280
don't you think I deserve
to have his heart?

234
00:17:55,280 --> 00:17:56,580
I'm going to make...

235
00:17:57,950 --> 00:17:59,780
this happiness mine, no matter what.

236
00:18:02,890 --> 00:18:06,060
For goodness sake. This girl...

237
00:18:07,690 --> 00:18:11,830
Honey, what are we going to do?
She really means it.

238
00:18:12,900 --> 00:18:14,400
My goodness.

239
00:18:14,730 --> 00:18:15,730
Min Jun.

240
00:18:19,040 --> 00:18:21,370
What's this? Why are you in a suit?

241
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:23,740
I wanted to go to the office.

242
00:18:24,480 --> 00:18:25,740
The office? Why?

243
00:18:26,010 --> 00:18:29,050
I thought my memory might come back
if I went somewhere familiar.

244
00:18:30,150 --> 00:18:32,480
But we agreed to take our time
finding your memories.

245
00:18:33,980 --> 00:18:38,260
Let's just go on a date
and see a movie.

246
00:18:39,860 --> 00:18:41,960
You knew about Chloe, didn't you?

247
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:44,160
What?

248
00:18:44,760 --> 00:18:47,830
I went to the police station.
They told me all about the accident.

249
00:18:49,070 --> 00:18:50,070
What?

250
00:18:50,970 --> 00:18:54,040
I learned that Chloe tried
to leak secrets but failed,

251
00:18:54,100 --> 00:18:57,980
and that we were in the accident
and both lost our memories.

252
00:19:00,640 --> 00:19:01,650
So?

253
00:19:03,680 --> 00:19:05,080
You and my mother...

254
00:19:07,450 --> 00:19:09,190
hid that from me
because you both were worried...

255
00:19:09,190 --> 00:19:10,690
she wasn't a very good person?

256
00:19:11,690 --> 00:19:12,760
That's right.

257
00:19:15,360 --> 00:19:17,330
I just didn't want to get into it.

258
00:19:17,530 --> 00:19:20,900
That's why I decided
I need to get my memory back sooner.

259
00:19:21,100 --> 00:19:23,900
I can't believe I worried about her
without knowing who she really was.

260
00:19:24,940 --> 00:19:26,570
Without my memory,

261
00:19:26,570 --> 00:19:29,370
I feel like
I'm just more confused and lost.

262
00:19:30,170 --> 00:19:32,910
But you could get another one
of your headaches,

263
00:19:33,240 --> 00:19:34,880
and you shouldn't push yourself
too hard.

264
00:19:35,080 --> 00:19:38,120
Even if I do get a sudden headache,
you'll be there to help me, right?

265
00:19:39,320 --> 00:19:41,250
I'll be okay because I have you.

266
00:19:49,890 --> 00:19:52,560
(Head of Division 1, Park Min Jun)

267
00:19:57,170 --> 00:19:58,370
What?

268
00:19:58,600 --> 00:20:01,040
May I take a look at this?

269
00:20:01,410 --> 00:20:04,340
Of course.
We prepared everything for you, sir.

270
00:20:07,710 --> 00:20:11,010
That's the proposal for
the new product's ad concept.

271
00:20:12,950 --> 00:20:15,550
Can I see the actual product?

272
00:20:16,290 --> 00:20:17,290
Of course.

273
00:20:20,990 --> 00:20:22,960
Here's our alkaline ionized water.

274
00:20:23,230 --> 00:20:25,100
Consumer feedback has been great.

275
00:20:25,260 --> 00:20:26,930
We expect sales to rise further...

276
00:20:26,930 --> 00:20:28,800
once Producer Shin's documentary airs.

277
00:20:29,330 --> 00:20:30,900
Producer Shin's documentary?

278
00:20:31,400 --> 00:20:33,570
Right, you forgot.

279
00:20:33,770 --> 00:20:35,540
- Chloe...
- Manager So!

280
00:20:37,940 --> 00:20:39,180
Is something bothering you?

281
00:20:39,510 --> 00:20:41,280
No, not at all.

282
00:20:42,750 --> 00:20:45,420
I was at a get-together last night
and ate way too much.

283
00:20:45,480 --> 00:20:49,420
You're always getting heartburn,
not just when you overeat.

284
00:20:52,720 --> 00:20:55,560
(Bion Tech)

285
00:21:02,230 --> 00:21:03,230
Here.

286
00:21:05,500 --> 00:21:08,210
I saw in the documents
that it's supposed to aid digestion.

287
00:21:08,410 --> 00:21:10,310
Thank you.

288
00:21:15,480 --> 00:21:18,450
Right.
About this product's ad concept...

289
00:21:18,720 --> 00:21:19,720
Yes?

290
00:21:19,720 --> 00:21:23,220
How about "The simple comfort
water brings to a busy life"?

291
00:21:23,390 --> 00:21:26,560
Not just as water to drink,
but water that soothes the system.

292
00:21:26,660 --> 00:21:29,290
I think that's a point
we should subtly show our customers.

293
00:21:29,290 --> 00:21:30,590
Goodness.

294
00:21:31,060 --> 00:21:33,460
You've still got it, sir.

295
00:21:33,730 --> 00:21:35,300
You think so?

296
00:21:37,700 --> 00:21:41,470
Please don't tell me
his memory is already coming back.

297
00:21:43,110 --> 00:21:45,610
Where's my mother's office?

298
00:21:45,680 --> 00:21:48,250
Since I'm here,
I'd like to see her office, too.

299
00:21:49,780 --> 00:21:51,050
Just head to the President's office.

300
00:21:52,450 --> 00:21:55,320
My mother became the president?
When? How did that happen?

301
00:22:01,690 --> 00:22:04,290
I'll wire the 60 million dollars.

302
00:22:06,530 --> 00:22:07,730
That won't be necessary.

303
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:10,800
Excuse me?

304
00:22:11,370 --> 00:22:13,770
Someone else came forward
with a better offer.

305
00:22:14,270 --> 00:22:16,540
I've already given them
the development rights.

306
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:24,150
What are you talking about?

307
00:22:32,520 --> 00:22:33,520
Good afternoon.

308
00:22:34,120 --> 00:22:36,460
I am the CEO of the investment firm
JKL Partners,

309
00:22:36,830 --> 00:22:38,300
James Lee.

310
00:22:39,930 --> 00:22:42,970
My firm has acquired
the development rights.

311
00:22:55,750 --> 00:22:56,750
What is this?

312
00:22:57,350 --> 00:22:59,880
So Kim Myung Hui has been dealing
with Assemblyman Kwon lately,

313
00:23:00,280 --> 00:23:01,280
leaving me completely
out of the loop?

314
00:23:01,690 --> 00:23:02,790
That's what I'm telling you.

315
00:23:04,490 --> 00:23:07,020
She's doing everything in her power
to push me out.

316
00:23:07,820 --> 00:23:10,430
I used to handle that kind of thing.
How dare he give it to Myung Hui?

317
00:23:12,200 --> 00:23:13,830
Now that I'm useless,

318
00:23:14,260 --> 00:23:15,970
is that why he's only looking out
for Kim Myung Hui?

319
00:23:16,770 --> 00:23:18,400
Well...

320
00:23:19,440 --> 00:23:20,770
would it be so bad
not to be needed anymore?

321
00:23:22,170 --> 00:23:25,080
- What?
- I've been thinking.

322
00:23:26,140 --> 00:23:29,310
Let's follow Hyun Jun
and go to the US.

323
00:23:30,180 --> 00:23:34,550
Hyun Jun gave up Adele
to find his own happiness in the US.

324
00:23:34,680 --> 00:23:37,420
So you should give up on Adele
and Chairman Park, too,

325
00:23:38,390 --> 00:23:40,960
and follow Hyun Jun
to the US with me.

326
00:23:41,020 --> 00:23:43,590
Are you out of your mind?
What nonsense is this?

327
00:23:43,660 --> 00:23:47,230
If you stay here, you're just going
to keep doing terrible things.

328
00:23:48,200 --> 00:23:51,740
If you risk someone's life again,
then I'll really have to...

329
00:23:54,340 --> 00:23:57,470
For Hyun Jun's sake,
I'll have to do what I have to do.

330
00:23:58,280 --> 00:23:59,340
Do what you have to do?

331
00:24:00,710 --> 00:24:02,110
And what exactly is that?

332
00:24:04,280 --> 00:24:05,280
What is it?

333
00:24:05,750 --> 00:24:07,520
Aren't you going to give me
a straight answer?

334
00:24:09,650 --> 00:24:10,990
President Kim Myung Hui...

335
00:24:12,020 --> 00:24:13,460
asked me to bring her proof.

336
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:16,690
Proof that you tried
to harm Park Min Jun.

337
00:24:17,290 --> 00:24:19,200
What?

338
00:24:20,700 --> 00:24:22,070
So promise me right now.

339
00:24:22,430 --> 00:24:24,400
Promise you'll go to the States
with Hyun Jun.

340
00:24:24,570 --> 00:24:25,700
If you don't,

341
00:24:26,440 --> 00:24:29,540
I'll hand over the proof
and get you kicked out.

342
00:24:29,540 --> 00:24:32,240
I'll make you go to the US with him.

343
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:39,120
Of all people,

344
00:24:39,980 --> 00:24:41,520
how could you do this to me?

345
00:24:42,790 --> 00:24:45,160
I'm doing this for you...

346
00:24:45,720 --> 00:24:47,690
- and for Hyun Jun's sake...
- You...

347
00:24:48,390 --> 00:24:50,490
saw everything I went through
to get here.

348
00:24:51,460 --> 00:24:54,930
From a maid treated less than human,
to the lady of Adele Group.

349
00:24:55,700 --> 00:24:59,100
I fought tooth and nail,
sacrificing my youth and my life.

350
00:24:59,600 --> 00:25:03,510
But you want me to get thrown out,
trampled on by Park Tae Ho?

351
00:25:03,540 --> 00:25:05,780
By handing me over to Kim Myung Hui,
no less?

352
00:25:06,940 --> 00:25:09,250
You dare...

353
00:25:09,980 --> 00:25:11,850
to disrespect my life like this?

354
00:25:12,420 --> 00:25:15,850
- That's not what I meant...
- Enough!

355
00:25:16,150 --> 00:25:17,750
You're no different
from Kim Myung Hui.

356
00:25:18,050 --> 00:25:21,160
You're just like
the rest of the world out to get me.

357
00:25:22,330 --> 00:25:25,660
Do you think that will scare me
into running away?

358
00:25:26,630 --> 00:25:29,630
No one gets to look down on
Oh Jung Ran.

359
00:25:31,900 --> 00:25:33,170
Please, Jung Ran.

360
00:25:34,340 --> 00:25:38,880
Please, just hear me out.

361
00:25:42,850 --> 00:25:45,250
What on earth is going on here?

362
00:25:52,460 --> 00:25:53,960
It's really quite simple.

363
00:25:54,760 --> 00:25:57,960
As CEO of an investment firm,
I learned of the opportunity,

364
00:25:57,960 --> 00:25:59,660
and I made a better offer
than Adele.

365
00:26:00,130 --> 00:26:02,230
It was enough to persuade
Assemblyman Kwon.

366
00:26:07,240 --> 00:26:11,040
He just snatched the one thing
Chairman Park worked on for so long.

367
00:26:12,240 --> 00:26:13,910
Did he just stumble into this
by coincidence?

368
00:26:14,540 --> 00:26:17,850
Or was this a calculated move
against Chairman Park?

369
00:26:22,150 --> 00:26:23,150
Chloe.

370
00:26:23,820 --> 00:26:25,760
Now I'm even starting to doubt...

371
00:26:26,420 --> 00:26:27,960
if you've really lost your memory.

372
00:26:28,890 --> 00:26:29,890
Chairman Park,

373
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:35,230
if you want this deal that badly,
I think I might be able to help.

374
00:26:36,000 --> 00:26:39,170
Could we speak alone for a moment?

375
00:26:50,510 --> 00:26:53,950
(Head of Division 2, Park Hyun Jun)

376
00:26:55,250 --> 00:26:57,220
(Sky Air, Hyun Jun Park, Chloe Lee)

377
00:27:00,990 --> 00:27:03,860
Give me everything you have.
Your family name, your title,

378
00:27:04,760 --> 00:27:05,830
and even your shares.

379
00:27:08,370 --> 00:27:10,770
In return, you'll get
the marriage you want...

380
00:27:14,240 --> 00:27:15,310
and me.

381
00:27:19,510 --> 00:27:21,610
(Head of Division 2, Park Hyun Jun)

382
00:27:28,220 --> 00:27:29,220
What's going on?

383
00:27:30,490 --> 00:27:33,860
Chloe is speaking privately
with Chairman Park right now.

384
00:27:34,660 --> 00:27:35,660
What?

385
00:27:36,060 --> 00:27:37,630
They aren't on the best of terms,

386
00:27:38,560 --> 00:27:39,630
so I'm a little worried.

387
00:27:40,230 --> 00:27:43,170
I hate to ask, but can you come over
and help Chloe out?

388
00:27:59,450 --> 00:28:00,450
Chloe.

389
00:28:01,920 --> 00:28:03,390
Are you sure she's lost her memory?

390
00:28:04,350 --> 00:28:05,360
Of course she has.

391
00:28:06,590 --> 00:28:09,560
You brought someone with amnesia
to a place like this,

392
00:28:10,260 --> 00:28:12,500
and you're just letting her meet
with the chairman alone?

393
00:28:13,200 --> 00:28:17,270
Chloe may have lost her memory,
but she's still smart and clever.

394
00:28:17,970 --> 00:28:20,140
From now on, she'll be by my side
helping with my business,

395
00:28:20,400 --> 00:28:21,770
so we agreed she would accompany me.

396
00:28:21,840 --> 00:28:24,840
And meeting with the Chairman...

397
00:28:25,180 --> 00:28:27,240
was something
Chloe requested herself.

398
00:28:27,680 --> 00:28:30,980
She had something important to say
and asked for a moment of his time.

399
00:28:34,180 --> 00:28:35,190
Ms. Kim!

400
00:28:37,990 --> 00:28:40,220
I have an urgent report.

401
00:28:41,830 --> 00:28:43,990
- Let's go to my office.
- Yes.

402
00:28:58,410 --> 00:29:01,680
If you'd like,
I'll try to persuade my father.

403
00:29:02,450 --> 00:29:05,750
I'll tell him it's a huge deal
and to partner with the Adele Group.

404
00:29:06,080 --> 00:29:09,020
You want to be partners?

405
00:29:09,720 --> 00:29:12,390
But I have two conditions.

406
00:29:13,290 --> 00:29:14,490
Two of them?

407
00:29:16,360 --> 00:29:17,360
First,

408
00:29:18,290 --> 00:29:21,700
I want you to apologize to me...

409
00:29:22,830 --> 00:29:26,170
for framing me for trying
to leak company secrets.

410
00:29:26,770 --> 00:29:27,840
Tell me that you're sorry.

411
00:29:29,140 --> 00:29:32,940
Bow your head and apologize,
just like I had to.

412
00:29:35,280 --> 00:29:38,780
Right. This can't be a coincidence.

413
00:29:39,320 --> 00:29:41,120
From the moment
you first came to Adele,

414
00:29:41,780 --> 00:29:43,690
have you been planning
this all along?

415
00:29:45,560 --> 00:29:48,090
You knew how much I put
into this project,

416
00:29:48,390 --> 00:29:51,160
and you snatched it away on purpose.

417
00:29:52,660 --> 00:29:53,660
Intentionally?

418
00:29:54,460 --> 00:29:56,170
Why are you so suspicious of me?

419
00:29:56,630 --> 00:30:00,200
I'm only bringing this up
because I really want to help you.

420
00:30:03,640 --> 00:30:06,780
You're lying about the amnesia too,
aren't you?

421
00:30:07,140 --> 00:30:08,850
You've been deceiving me
all this time,

422
00:30:09,310 --> 00:30:11,780
just to sabotage my business?

423
00:30:15,950 --> 00:30:17,090
Father!

424
00:30:21,160 --> 00:30:24,430
What are you doing to Chloe again?

425
00:30:24,930 --> 00:30:26,130
If you have any humanity,

426
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:28,630
you can't do this to Chloe.

427
00:30:29,500 --> 00:30:30,500
Again?

428
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:33,040
Stay out of this
because you don't know anything!

429
00:30:33,670 --> 00:30:37,040
She's a viper who's intentionally
trying to ruin my business.

430
00:30:38,170 --> 00:30:40,180
She dares to get in the way
of me, Park Tae Ho.

431
00:30:40,810 --> 00:30:42,280
I won't just stand by
and let that happen.

432
00:30:43,110 --> 00:30:44,750
Then you leave me no choice.

433
00:30:45,820 --> 00:30:47,450
I'll be the one to protect Chloe.

434
00:30:49,890 --> 00:30:50,890
What?

435
00:30:52,390 --> 00:30:53,390
You...

436
00:30:54,920 --> 00:30:55,990
You...

437
00:31:10,340 --> 00:31:12,210
I want to protect you
from my father.

438
00:31:13,940 --> 00:31:14,940
Honestly,

439
00:31:16,110 --> 00:31:18,350
I don't really get
this whole revenge thing.

440
00:31:20,920 --> 00:31:22,750
But seeing my father hurt you...

441
00:31:25,390 --> 00:31:26,860
is something I can't bear.

442
00:31:35,970 --> 00:31:37,100
Then...

443
00:31:38,840 --> 00:31:41,700
does this mean
you'll accept my offer?

444
00:31:45,210 --> 00:31:46,580
I'll give you...

445
00:31:50,510 --> 00:31:51,550
everything I have.

446
00:32:00,960 --> 00:32:02,060
Are these the test results?

447
00:32:02,760 --> 00:32:05,360
Yes, hurry up and open it.

448
00:32:06,730 --> 00:32:09,470
I was so nervous,
I couldn't bring myself to open it.

449
00:32:45,100 --> 00:32:48,170
(Pearl in Red)

450
00:32:48,340 --> 00:32:50,610
What were you doing
while Assemblyman Kwon...

451
00:32:50,610 --> 00:32:51,670
was betraying us?

452
00:32:51,940 --> 00:32:54,980
You promised perfection.
What is this mess?

453
00:32:54,980 --> 00:32:56,010
I'm sorry.

454
00:32:57,210 --> 00:33:00,380
I knew I should've left this
to Oh Jung Ran.

455
00:33:00,620 --> 00:33:04,050
Kim Myung Hui. I heard you
threatened Mr. Song for evidence.

456
00:33:04,220 --> 00:33:07,090
How dare you threaten my people
behind my back?

457
00:33:07,090 --> 00:33:08,090
Your people?

458
00:33:08,160 --> 00:33:11,760
What are you waiting for?
Show this to Chairman Park.

459
00:33:11,890 --> 00:33:14,560
This is enough to make him divorce
Oh Jung Ran in a heartbeat.

460
00:33:15,130 --> 00:33:17,100
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
